'''Corellian Gambit''' was a style of [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]] play that originated from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. Similar to Corellian Spike, this variant of Sabacc is played closest to 0 as possible. However, Corellian Gambit uses a standard Sabacc Deck.

